Name: Fastraq
About the game: Fastraq is a sci-fi based high-speed anti-gravity racing game. Drive on roller coaster like tracks, overtake your opponents and engage in combat. Experience tight turns, 360 degree loops and intense combat. Hyper-sonic mode In hyper-sonic mode you race against 14 AI opponents at speeds of 2000 mph on roller coaster like loopy and curvy tracks. Hyper-combat mode In hyper-combat mode, you engage in intense machine to machine combat at speeds of 2000 mph with 14 AI opponents. You can use variety of weapons like plasma weapon or bullets to destroy your opponent. Campaign Dive straight into the campaign mode. Campaign consists of 20 unique levels. Each level is more difficult than the previous one. And you need to win a level to unlock the next one. Vehicles There are six different vehicles to choose from. Depending on the track you want to race, choose your vehicle and strategize your race to win it. Features Works well with a controller Intense combat racing Competitive AI Roller coaster like tracks 5 game modes 5 levels of difficulty
